maemo-translate (0.1.6) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Copy/Paste to/from clipboard buttons, and a clear button
  * Word completion on the 'from' translation textbox. Currently does *not* work on Maemo (why?)
  * Cyrillic transliteration to Latin
  * During startup, fallback to a default model when the requested model is not present
  * Clear results when input is empty
  * Load environment from file during Debug
  * Install a desktop icon
  * Bump version

